member.param:
An array of FeatureLevels, which determine the order of feature levels to attempt to create. 
If set to null, the following array of feature levels will be used: 

   {
       FeatureLevel_11_0,
       FeatureLevel_10_1,
       FeatureLevel_10_0,
       FeatureLevel_9_3,
       FeatureLevel_9_2,
       FeatureLevel_9_1,
   };

